abilityDescription: Peachey's chaotic gamedev mind turns every code bug into a cosmic crisis, ironically causing more bugs while trying to fix them.
attackDescription: Unleashes an overwhelming barrage of 'vibecoding' memes and tech nonsense that leaves opponents utterly confused and begging for clarity. Peachey's tweets get way too much hype for pure lunacy.
description: With a 'deranged gamedev' and 'shitposter' profile describing lost lunacy, the ability reflects chaotic coding irony. The attack is based on their most viral tweet about 'vibecoding', which garnered massive engagement but is nonsensical to most, fitting the psyop type. Their high follower count and verified ultra tier merits strong HP and attack damage. They resist psyop attacks (confusing/misleading content) but are weak to roast because biting criticism can pierce their lunatic facade.
